To make your pharmacy platform **more interactive and engaging**, consider adding these **UI components**:  

---

### **1. Search & Filtering**  
✅ **Auto-Suggest Search Bar** – Predictive search for medicines with quick links to product pages.  
✅ **Filters & Sorting** – Sort by price, category, brand, or availability.  

---

### **2. Interactive Product Display**  
✅ **Quick View Modal** – Allows users to see product details in a popup without leaving the page.  
✅ **Hover Effects on Product Cards** – Show extra details like price, discount, or “Add to Cart” on hover.  
✅ **Image Zoom** – Hover or click to zoom into medicine packaging.  
✅ **Interactive Rating & Reviews** – Users can upvote helpful reviews.  

---

### **3. Shopping Cart & Checkout Enhancements**  
✅ **Mini Cart Drawer** – Slides out when adding a product instead of redirecting to the cart page.  
✅ **Progress Bar in Checkout** – Shows the steps: Cart → Address → Payment → Confirmation.  
✅ **Coupon Code Input with Live Discount Calculation** – Instantly applies discounts.  
✅ **One-Click Reorder Button** – Helps users quickly repurchase previous medicines.  

---

### **4. User Engagement & Assistance**  
✅ **Live Chat or AI Chatbot** – Assist users with medicine recommendations and FAQs.  
✅ **Medicine Reminder Feature** – Allow users to set medication reminders via email or notifications.  
✅ **Prescription Upload with Drag & Drop** – Simplifies prescription submission.  
✅ **Order Tracking Timeline** – Visual progress bar for order status (e.g., Processing → Shipped → Out for Delivery).  

---

### **5. Interactive Elements for Trust & Personalization**  
✅ **Dark Mode Toggle** – Enhances accessibility.  
✅ **Lottie Animations** – Small animations for loading screens or success messages.  
✅ **User Dashboard with Personalized Suggestions** – Based on past purchases or search history.  
✅ **Gamification Elements** – Reward points or badges for repeat purchases.  

---
